## FINAL MUST-PASS CHECKLIST

- [ ] All 8 required sections present: Header, Business Context, Scope, Requirements, Technical Overview, Risk Assessment, Timeline, Feature Breakdown
- [ ] Success metrics are measurable and specific (not vague)
- [ ] Scope boundaries clearly defined with explicit In/Out of Scope lists
- [ ] Feature breakdown present with at least 1 feature identified
- [ ] Risk assessment includes mitigation strategies
- [ ] No OPSEC violations (internal URLs, credentials, personal emails)
- [ ] Provenance footer appended with timestamp
- [ ] Markdown formatting follows structure requirements
